From: Ian Rogers <irogers@google.com>
Date: Wed, 2 Apr 2025 13:15:48 -0700
Subject: perf evlist: Make groups visible in evlist__format_evsels() output
Git-commit: 583dc500d153d90260435c68a393fd3b5d44b18e
Patch-mainline: v6.16-rc1
References: perf-sle16.1-v6.19-userspace-update

Make groups visible in output:

Before:

{cycles,instructions} ->
cpu_atom/cycles/,cpu_atom/instructions/,cpu_core/cycles/,cpu_core/instructions/

After:

{cycles,instructions} ->
{cpu_atom/cycles/,cpu_atom/instructions/},{cpu_core/cycles/,cpu_core/instructions/}

Committer testing:

Before:

  root@number:~# perf record -e '{cycles,instructions,cache-misses}' /tmp/bla
  Failed to collect 'cycles,instructions,cache-misses' for the '/tmp/bla' workload: Permission denied
  root@number:~#

After:

  root@number:~# perf record -e '{cycles,instructions,cache-misses}' /tmp/bla
  Failed to collect '{cycles,instructions,cache-misses}' for the '/tmp/bla' workload: Permission denied
  root@number:~#

